  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I think the contrast for the two tabs is a little low, so it looks like half the
stuff is under the unchosen tag. Maybe if the selected tab had an outline it
would help. The very light blue, extremely light blue and white that whispers of
blue is just too tricky to see until you've been looking for a while. Perhaps
the light green and the light blue from the logo could be used thematically
throughout the site to signify "for users" and "for projects/mentors"</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
