Current design-type thoughts for self: kill the dang tabs, kill the detailed
feature promises, make things less slick (but still pretty), make /about/ text /
OH's mission more prominent. Might tone down the hatching?

See <a href="http://www.givewell.org/">http://www.givewell.org/</a> and <a href="http://git-scm.com">http://git-scm.com</a> for inspiration.

Also see <a href="https://openhatch.org/bugs/issue197">https://openhatch.org/bugs/issue197</a></pre>
